  "description": "Indulge in the captivating beauty of this lab-grown ruby ring, set in high-quality S925 sterling silver. Known for its durability and hypoallergenic properties, S925 silver ensures a comfortable and lasting fit, while the elegant design radiates sophistication and style.\n\nAt the heart of this ring is a stunning 8x11mm, 4.99-carat oval-cut lab-grown ruby, known for its deep red hue that symbolizes passion and love. The ruby is encircled by a sparkling halo of round-cut accent stones, adding brilliance and elegance to the design. What makes this piece truly unique are the two emerald-cut stones on either side of the band, including one exquisite emerald-cut stone on each side of the ring, making this a rare and exceptional design. The total weight of the accent stones is 5.603 carats, giving the ring a dazzling effect. Weighing 5.22 grams, this piece offers a comfortable yet luxurious feel. and is available in sizes 5 to 7.5 (standard U.S. sizing). Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings have an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Ruby Center Stone: A striking 8x11mm, 4.99-carat oval-cut ruby with a rich, passionate red color.\n\nHalo of Round-Cut Accent Stones: A circle of round-cut stones encircles the ruby, amplifying its brilliance.\n\nEmerald-Cut Accent Stones: Two stunning emerald-cut stones (one on each side) add a rare and unique touch to the design, totaling 5.603 carats.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Hypoallergenic, tarnish-resistant, and durable for long-lasting wear.\n\nComfortable and Luxurious: Weighs 5.22 grams, offering a substantial yet wearable fit.\n\nThis exceptional ruby ring, with its captivating halo and emerald-cut accents, is a perfect choice for those seeking a luxurious and unique piece that stands out.",
